name: Rising Tides
description: The tides across Elysium Perdita are rising and so are our ships, as we look out at the shores we see a mirror to our souls - poem ‘Man & The Sea’ by Charles Baudelaire - animated from paintings ‘Ships in Distress off a Rocky Coast’ by Ludolf Backhuysen c. 1667 and Rubens’ ‘The Fall of Phaeton’ c. 1604 - produced and performed by Laurence Fuller @laurencefuller
